Validation Queries
Query 1: Pick 10 sample records from DEV and check all key fields

-- DEV: Get 10 sample records to validate field-by-field against PROD
SELECT 
    serialnumber,
    aep_opco,
    aep_usage_dt,
    aep_channel_id,
    aep_raw_uom,
    aep_derived_uom,
    endtimeperiod,
    starttimeperiod,
    value,
    aep_raw_value,
    scalarfloat,
    aep_premise_nb,
    aep_service_point,
    aep_srvc_dlvry_id,
    aep_mtr_pnt_nb,
    aep_tarf_pnt_nb,
    aep_devicecode,
    aep_meter_program,
    aep_srvc_qlty_idntfr,
    name_register,
    aep_sec_per_intrvl,
    aep_endtime_utc,
    aep_acct_cls_cd,
    aep_acct_type_cd,
    aep_city,
    aep_zip,
    aep_state,
    authority,
    hdp_update_user,
    aep_meter_bucket
FROM usage_nonvee.reading_ivl_nonvee_oh
WHERE aep_usage_dt IN ('2026-03-23', '2026-03-24')
  AND aep_premise_nb IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 10;
Query 2: Take those same 10 records and validate in PROD
Copy the serialnumber + endtimeperiod + aep_channel_id from above and run in PROD:


